@startuml
title Registration Protocol
autonumber

actor Admin
actor Client
participant "Paranoia Server\n/reg" as Server
database "Server user config" as Config

Admin -> Admin: Generate Ed25519 admin signature\nover username || user_pubkey_b64
Admin --> Client: Send admin_sig_b64 out-of-band
Client -> Server: POST /reg\n{username, pub_key, admin_sig}
Server -> Server: Decode user pubkey and admin signature
Server -> Config: Load configured admin public key
Server -> Server: Verify admin signature
Server -> Config: Check username is not registered
Server -> Config: Save username -> user public key
Server --> Client: {success: true, message: "OK"}

@enduml
